{"id":248,"parent_id":245,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":248,"title":"1 Samuel 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Sam.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 3"],[".studySummary",["i","The Lord calls Samuel—The house of Eli will not be purged by sacrifices and offerings—Samuel is recognized as a prophet by all Israel—The Lord appears to him."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.1","order":"02.10.003.20817"},["b","1"],"And the child Samuel ministered unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"before Eli. And the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"was precious in those days;",["i","there was"],"no open",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"vision"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.2","order":"02.10.003.20818"},["b","2"],"And it came to pass at that time, when Eli",["i","was"],"laid down in his place, and his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"eyes"],"began to wax dim,",["i","that"],"he could not see;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.3","order":"02.10.003.20819"},["b","3"],"And ere the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"lamp"],"of God went out in the temple of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", where the ark of God",["i","was,"],"and Samuel was laid down",["i","to sleep;"]],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.4","order":"02.10.003.20820"},["b","4"],"That the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"called Samuel: and he answered, Here",["i","am"],"I."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.5","order":"02.10.003.20821"},["b","5"],"And he ran unto Eli, and said, Here",["i","am"],"I; for thou calledst me. And he said, I called not; lie down again. And he went and lay down."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.6","order":"02.10.003.20822"},["b","6"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"called yet again, Samuel. And Samuel arose and went to Eli, and said, Here",["i","am"],"I; for thou didst call me. And he answered, I called not, my son; lie down again."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.7","order":"02.10.003.20823"},["b","7"],"Now Samuel did not yet know the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", neither was the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"yet revealed unto him."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.8","order":"02.10.003.20824"},["b","8"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"called Samuel again the third time. And he arose and went to Eli, and said, Here",["i","am"],"I; for thou didst call me. And Eli perceived that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had called the child."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.9","order":"02.10.003.20825"},["b","9"],"Therefore Eli said unto Samuel, Go, lie down: and it shall be, if he call thee, that thou shalt say, Speak,",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; for thy servant heareth. So Samuel went and lay down in his place."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.10","order":"02.10.003.20826"},["b","10"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"stood"],", and called as at other times, Samuel, Samuel. Then Samuel answered, Speak; for thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"servant"],"heareth."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.11","order":"02.10.003.20827"},["b","11"],"¶And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said to Samuel, Behold, I will do a thing in Israel, at which both the ears of every one that heareth it shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"tingle"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.12","order":"02.10.003.20828"},["b","12"],"In that day I will perform",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"against"],"Eli all",["i","things"],"which I have spoken concerning his house: when I begin, I will also make an end."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.13","order":"02.10.003.20829"},["b","13"],"For I have told him that I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"judge"],"his house for ever for the iniquity which he knoweth; because his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"sons"],"made themselves vile, and he",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"restrained"],"them not."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.14","order":"02.10.003.20830"},["b","14"],"And therefore I have sworn unto the house of Eli, that the iniquity of Eli’s house shall not be purged with sacrifice nor offering for ever."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.15","order":"02.10.003.20831"},["b","15"],"¶And Samuel lay until the morning, and opened the doors of the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],". And Samuel",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"feared"],"to shew Eli the vision."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.16","order":"02.10.003.20832"},["b","16"],"Then Eli called Samuel, and said, Samuel, my son. And he answered, Here",["i","am"],"I."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.17","order":"02.10.003.20833"},["b","17"],"And he said, What",["i","is"],"the thing that",["i","the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"]],"hath said unto thee? I pray thee hide",["i","it"],"not from me: God do so to thee, and more also, if thou hide",["i","any"],"thing from me of all the things that he said unto thee."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.18","order":"02.10.003.20834"},["b","18"],"And Samuel told him every whit, and hid nothing from him. And he said, It",["i","is"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": let him do what seemeth him good."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.19","order":"02.10.003.20835"},["b","19"],"¶And Samuel",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"grew"],", and the",["span.smallCaps",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"Lord"]],"was",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"with"],"him, and did let none of his words",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_19d"},"fall"],"to the ground."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.20","order":"02.10.003.20836"},["b","20"],"And all Israel from Dan even to Beer-sheba knew that Samuel",["i","was"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"established"],["i","to be"],"a prophet of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.21","order":"02.10.003.20837"},["b","21"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"appeared"],"again in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"Shiloh"],": for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"revealed himself to Samuel in Shiloh by the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"word"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.1a","order":"02.10.003.20838"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/74.9"},"Ps. 74:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/8.11"},"Amos 8:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.14.13-14"},"Morm. 1:14 (13–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.21"},"JS—H 1:21"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/revelation"},"TG Revelation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vision"},"Vision"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.2a","order":"02.10.003.20840"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/4.15"},"1 Sam. 4:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.3a","order":"02.10.003.20842"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/27.20.20-21"},"Ex. 27:20 (20–21)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/24.2.2-3"},"Lev. 24:2 (2–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.10a","order":"02.10.003.20844"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/1.11.8-15"},"1 Ne. 1:11 (8–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/110.2.2-3"},"D&C 110:2 (2–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.17"},"JS—H 1:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.10b","order":"02.10.003.20846"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/servant"},"TG Servant"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.11a","order":"02.10.003.20848"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.12"},"2 Kgs. 21:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.3"},"Jer. 19:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.3"},"3 Ne. 11:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.2.1-2"},"D&C 1:2 (1–2)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.12a","order":"02.10.003.20850"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/2.31.30-36"},"1 Sam. 2:31 (30–36)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.13a","order":"02.10.003.20852"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.3.3-8"},"Ezek. 7:3 (3–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.13b","order":"02.10.003.20854"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/2.12"},"1 Sam. 2:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/2.12.12-13"},"1 Ne. 2:12 (12–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/27.8.7-37"},"Mosiah 27:8 (7–37)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/5.16"},"Moses 5:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.13c","order":"02.10.003.20856"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/68.25"},"D&C 68:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/93.42.40-50"},"93:42 (40–50)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-children-responsibilities-toward"},"TG Family, Children, Responsibilities toward"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.15a","order":"02.10.003.20858"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/60.2.2-3"},"D&C 60:2 (2–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.19a","order":"02.10.003.20860"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/2.26"},"1 Sam. 2:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/2.52"},"Luke 2:52"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.19b","order":"02.10.003.20862"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/9.15.15-20"},"1 Sam. 9:15 (15–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.19c","order":"02.10.003.20864"},["b","19c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/6.27"},"Josh. 6:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"19d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.19d","order":"02.10.003.20866"},["b","19d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/10.10"},"2 Kgs. 10:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.20a","order":"02.10.003.20868"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/called-of-god"},"TG Called of God"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-authority"},"Priesthood, Authority"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.21a","order":"02.10.003.20870"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/3.13.6-16"},"Ether 3:13 (6–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.54.53-54"},"D&C 107:54 (53–54)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/2.19.6,19"},"Abr. 2:19 (6, 19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.21b","order":"02.10.003.20872"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/18.1"},"Josh. 18:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"21c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.21c","order":"02.10.003.20874"},["b","21c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-messenger-of-the-covenant"},"TG Jesus Christ, Messenger of the Covenant"],"."]]}
